[
    {
        "text": "Hi, everybody, and welcome.",
        "start": 0.189,
        "duration": 2.306
    },
    {
        "text": "In this video, we’re going to talk about\n‘this’ and ‘that’.",
        "start": 2.495,
        "duration": 4.981
    },
    {
        "text": "Now ‘this’ and ‘that’ are used to talk about nouns",
        "start": 7.476,
        "duration": 5.163
    },
    {
        "text": "that are close to us, near or far away.",
        "start": 12.639,
        "duration": 4.671
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 17.31,
        "duration": 0.753
    },
    {
        "text": "So let’s look at the board.",
        "start": 18.063,
        "duration": 2.426
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a flower.”",
        "start": 20.489,
        "duration": 3.713
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, we use ‘this’ to talk about one noun, “a flower”, that is close.",
        "start": 24.202,
        "duration": 7.845
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 32.047,
        "duration": 0.692
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a flower.”",
        "start": 32.739,
        "duration": 2.071
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s not far.",
        "start": 34.81,
        "duration": 1.435
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s close.",
        "start": 36.245,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "“That is a flower.”",
        "start": 38.095,
        "duration": 3.233
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, we use ‘that’ to talk about one noun that’s far away.",
        "start": 41.328,
        "duration": 6.242
    },
    {
        "text": "So, “That… that is a flower”.",
        "start": 47.57,
        "duration": 5.509
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 53.079,
        "duration": 0.825
    },
    {
        "text": "For another example…",
        "start": 53.904,
        "duration": 2.006
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a marker.”",
        "start": 55.91,
        "duration": 2.903
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s close to me.",
        "start": 58.813,
        "duration": 2.047
    },
    {
        "text": "But “That… that is a marker”.",
        "start": 60.86,
        "duration": 4.69
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s far away.",
        "start": 65.55,
        "duration": 2.137
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let’s move on to the next part.",
        "start": 67.687,
        "duration": 3.269
    },
    {
        "text": "So we know…",
        "start": 70.956,
        "duration": 1.374
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a flower.”",
        "start": 72.33,
        "duration": 2.948
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 75.278,
        "duration": 0.953
    },
    {
        "text": "And “That is a flower... that”.",
        "start": 76.231,
        "duration": 3.919
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, “Is this a flower”?",
        "start": 80.15,
        "duration": 3.228
    },
    {
        "text": "“What is it?”",
        "start": 83.378,
        "duration": 1.415
    },
    {
        "text": "“It’s a chair.”",
        "start": 84.793,
        "duration": 1.537
    },
    {
        "text": "So we have to use the negative.",
        "start": 86.33,
        "duration": 2.206
    },
    {
        "text": "“This isn’t a flower.”",
        "start": 88.536,
        "duration": 2.654
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s close by, but it isn’t a flower.",
        "start": 91.19,
        "duration": 4.23
    },
    {
        "text": "‘isn’t’ is a contraction for ‘is not’.",
        "start": 95.42,
        "duration": 4.336
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 99.756,
        "duration": 0.764
    },
    {
        "text": "“This isn’t a flower.”",
        "start": 100.52,
        "duration": 2.562
    },
    {
        "text": "“This is a chair.”",
        "start": 103.082,
        "duration": 3.141
    },
    {
        "text": "“That isn’t a flower.”",
        "start": 106.223,
        "duration": 2.936
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s far away, so we say “that”.",
        "start": 109.159,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, we have ‘isn’t’, ‘a flower’.",
        "start": 111.919,
        "duration": 3.31
    },
    {
        "text": "“That’s a chair.”",
        "start": 115.229,
        "duration": 2.468
    },
    {
        "text": "And let’s take another example.",
        "start": 117.697,
        "duration": 2.513
    },
    {
        "text": "“This isn’t a pencil.”",
