        "start": 123.491,
        "duration": 1.979
    },
    {
        "text": "And…",
        "start": 125.47,
        "duration": 0.961
    },
    {
        "text": "“That isn’t a pencil.”",
        "start": 126.431,
        "duration": 3.262
    },
    {
        "text": "“That is a marker.”",
        "start": 129.693,
        "duration": 2.425
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, let’s move on to the next part.",
        "start": 132.118,
        "duration": 3.552
    },
    {
        "text": "Now we’re going to learn how to use\n‘this’ and ‘that’ in a question.",
        "start": 135.67,
        "duration": 5.539
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 141.209,
        "duration": 0.63
    },
    {
        "text": "So we know, “This is a flower”.",
        "start": 141.839,
        "duration": 3.91
    },
    {
        "text": "When we make a question, we have to switch.",
        "start": 145.749,
        "duration": 3.169
    },
    {
        "text": "We put the ‘be’ verb first.",
        "start": 148.918,
        "duration": 2.393
    },
    {
        "text": "So it becomes, “Is this a flower?”.",
        "start": 151.311,
        "duration": 4.257
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, it’s close by.",
        "start": 155.568,
        "duration": 1.703
    },
